project_descr: BCtA is a global advocacy platform that works to accelerate progress towards the SDGs by  supporting companies to develop inclusive business models that offer the potential for both commercial success and development impact.

outputs.output_descr: BCtA will build on its strong member base by further raising awareness of IB practices and contributions to SDGs; providing recognition to quality IBs and supporting companies through tools and training.
donor_name: SWISS AGENCY FOR DEVELOPMENT AND COOPERATION - SDC
